snippet.title: Brian Tyler Cohen
snippet.description:
Brian Tyler Cohen is a progressive political host known for finding the top breaking political content online. Every video is followed by in-depth commentary to keep you informed on exactly what's going on, why it's important, and how it affects you-- always in a way that you can understand. It doesn't matter if you're a DC insider or just interested in the news, young or old, progressive or moderate, this channel is dedicated to giving a clear, concise, and honest look at what's happening in politics right now.

Whether debunking bad faith talking points, propaganda, or outright lies, Brian works seven days a week to report the news as it happens, backed up by facts. It's no-BS news that gets right to the point from a source you can trust.
